info.title: Eventbrite Webhooks API
info.description: The API for managing Eventbrite webhooks.

get.summary: Returns the list of webhook objects that belong to the authenticated user.
get.description: Returns the list of webhook objects that belong to the authenticated user.

post.summary: Creates a webhook for the authenticated user.
post.description: Creates a webhook for the authenticated user.

parameters.name: actions
parameters.description: Determines what actions the hook is triggered for.An empty list means that all actions trigger a webhook post.See below for a more complete description.

parameters.name: endpoint_url
parameters.description: The target URL of the Webhook subscription.

parameters.name: event_id
parameters.description: The ID of the event that triggers this webhook. Leave blank for all events.

get.summary: Returns a webhook for the specified webhook as webhook.
